Summary: New option: planner-use-plan-pages
Keywords: 

	* planner.el (planner-use-plan-pages): New option. Yes, you can
	turn plan pages off as well. Try not to have planner-use-day-pages
	and planner-use-plan-pages off at the same time.
	(planner-create-task-from-buffer): Follow planner-use-day-pages
	and planner-use-plan-pages.
	(planner-create-task): Follow planner-use-day-pages and
	planner-use-plan-pages.

	* planner.texi (Variables to Customize): Document planner-use-plan-pages.
